t our ability to make causal claims in this\nanalysis, MTPs are a powerful and underutilized tool for studying the effects\nof continuous exposures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Oct 2021 21:17:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 05:42:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 16 Mar 2022 16:56:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-17"}
