},|\\eta^c|_{L_x^2}=O(|t|^{-1})$ and $|v_2^c|_{L_x^2}=O(t^{-2})$\nas $|t|\\gg1$. Additional decay of $tv_1^c,t^2v_2^c$ in $L_x^2L_t^q$,\n$q\\in(2,\\infty]$, is obtained after leading asymptotic terms are removed, which\nare in the forms of $t$-dependent translations in $x_1$ of certain functions of\n$x$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2021 02:32:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 Mar 2022 20:52:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 12 Jan 2023 16:49:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-13"}
