 -3.05\\pm0.36$ compatible between themselves, in the frequency\nrange 23-30 GHz. Results also seem to indicate that the SED gets steeper from\nlow to high Galactic latitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2021 11:00:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2022 10:12:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-07"}
