vskite as compared to bare CdSe/CdZnS QDs. At high doping\nlevels, this work opens the route to hybrid-based LEDs. Low-doping content\nwould lead to hybrid single-photon sources embedded in field-effect devices to\nserve as an alternative to solid-state QDs and help building nanophotonic\ndevices with high-quantum-yield CdSe-based QDs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2021 12:43:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
