e\nmethod is further validated on an experimental data set using modal analysis on\na simple free-free beam, demonstrating the efficacy of the proposed methodology\nas an appropriate candidate for modeling practical dynamical systems despite\nhaving no access to internal state measurements and treating the full model as\na black-box.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2021 14:32:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
